Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Data Science techniques to analyze human mobility using mobile phone datasets. This falls under the category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) as well as the sub-category of Signal Processing (cs.SD) for processing the mobile phone data. Additionally, the paper discusses applications of mobility analyses for urban planning (cs.CY), building delay tolerant networks (cs.CE), and generating epidemiologic risk maps (cs.CR).
